orm=\"author\">Numen.</author> </bibl> ap. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg2018.tlg001:14:8\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Eus.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\">PE</title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">14.8</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n53926.1\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> generally, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">guess</tr_>, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">οὐ γὰρ ἄν κοτε κατέδοξα ἔνθεν ἦν</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">should</tr_> never <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">have guessed</tr_> whose son he was, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:111\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hdt.\">Hdt.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.111</biblScope></bibl>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}